\newlabel{fig:crosslingual}{{6}{10}{Cross lingual layer wise mean projection for XLM-RoBERTa Base across Spanish, Arabic, and Tigrinya. Remarkably, the architecture encodes bias with an identical trajectory (peaking exactly at Layer~9) regardless of the language's resource level}{figure.caption.10}{}}
